---
// Why Us section component
---

<section id="why" class="section section-alt" aria-label="Why choose Black62">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why Choose Black62</p>
      <h2 class="display-2 silver">Built on trust. Engineered for scale.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <span class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg></span>
        <h3>Experienced Management</h3>
        <p>Over two decades of combined sector expertise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card reveal delay-1">
        <span class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg></span>
        <h3>Reliable Supply Chain</h3>
        <p>Long-standing producer and transporter relationships.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card reveal delay-2">
        <span class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.82z"/><line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7"/></svg></span>
        <h3>Competitive Pricing</h3>
        <p>Transparent, efficient, and commercially fair.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card reveal delay-3">
        <span class="feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></span>
        <h3>Full Compliance</h3>
        <p>SARS, B-BBEE, and regulatory alignment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
